Welcome to Fast Food restaurant
Since Our Grandpa Dickhead started fast food resaturant in 1898 he always insisted using fresh ingredients to serve dishes to our customers.
I know, I know, it's super touching.
After restaurnt handed down to me,(current owner), I decided to change some old-fashioned rules such as "no more fresh ingredients", "no more cheap foods", etc.
As result, our long-run buisness has been ruined as you can see at photo, there is no even single life form that can be found.
